mkdir backend
cd backend
npm init : to install node modules 
npm install dependencies (express mongoose ...)

 npm i express mongoose  cors
 npm install dotenv : to load global variables from .env thatnks to proccess.env
 npm install --save-dev nodemon : to run the backend
 we use cors to access our routes from any origin we can use it with all routes or with some routes and the implementation differs 
.env contains global variables 
port : the port in which server is running 
DB-Uri : database uri local or atlas  
